title: The Dennis Prager Radio Show SEP-02-2013 MON
description:
The Dennis Prager Radio Show SEP-02-2013 MON







Prager 20120902  3 Labor Day, Pt. 3

Prager H3: Dennis takes your calls to find out: What is your labor?
 Callers include...
 a tree czar, a phone bill auditor, an avocado diva, an autopsy assistant, 
 an infomercial product inventor, a builder of guitar amplifiers,
 and a P.I.


Prager 20120902  2 Labor Day, Pt. 2

Prager H2: Dennis takes your calls to find out:
 What is your labor? Callers include...
 a recruiter for workforce development, an accounting software instructor,
 a tomahawk cruise missile mission planner, a stain glass window maker,
 a firearm safety instructor, a stay at home dad who hates doing it,
 and another stay at home dad who loves it.


Prager 20120902  1 Labor Day, Pt. 1

Prager H1: Dennis takes your calls to find out: What is your labor?
 Callers include...
 an appraiser of high value homes, a ballroom dancing instructor,
 a pharmacy tech, and a dental hygienist.
